t-program" class="footer-links">Fast Track Career Pilot Program</a></li><li class="footer-list-item"><a href="/programs/gateway-career-pilot-program" class="footer-links">Gateway Career Pilot Program</a></li><li class="footer-list-item"><a href="/programs/philadelphia-cirrus-pilot-training" class="footer-links">Cirrus Platinum Training Center</a></li></ul></div></div></div></section><section class="primary-section black-footer"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer primary-container w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid footer-grid"><div class="footer-container centered-fotter"><img src="images/flygateway-logowhite.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="image-5"/></div><div id="w-node-_8d281c61-8749-e8bc-4232-4a13d5fe4e47-d5fe4e42" class="footer-container centered-fotter"><div class="copywrite">© flyGATEWAY 2025</div></div><div class="footer-container centered-fotter"><a href="/policies/privacy-policy" class="link">Privacy Policy</a><div class="white-footer-text">/</div><a href="/policies/accessibility" class="link">Accessibility</a></div></div></div><div class="menu-overlay"><a href="#" class="closebutton w-inline-block"><img src="images/close-bold-svgrepo-com.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></a><div class="menu-container"><div class="_5050-contain-na"><div class="_50-nav-side"><a href="/programs" class="navigation-menu-link w-inline-block"><div>Career Pilot Programs</div></a><a href="/programs/philadelphia-cirrus-pilot-training" class="navigation-menu-link w-inline-block"><div>Cirrus Pilot Training</div></a><div data-hover="false" data-delay="200" data-w-id="c4756568-e03c-8133-5fdb-9245feb52b07" class="navigation-menu-link w-dropdown"><div class="dropdown-toggle w-dropdown-toggle"><div>University Partners</div></div><nav class="dropdown-list-2 w-dropdown-list"><a href="/university-partners/marywood-university" class="dropdown-link w-dropdown-link">Marywood Universirty</a><a href="/university-partners/liberty-university-aviation-pennsylvania" class="dropdown-link w-dropdown-